detailed_optimizations.code_changes:
将 /9.0 改为乘以预计算常量 inv9；在 i 循环内缓存相邻三行指针，避免重复二维下标寻址；将内层表达式拆成局部标量，帮助寄存器分配。示例：
const DATA_TYPE inv9 = (DATA_TYPE)1.0 / (DATA_TYPE)9.0;
for (t = 0; t < tsteps; ++t) {
  for (i = 1; i < n-1; ++i) {
    DATA_TYPE *rowm = A[i-1];
    DATA_TYPE *row  = A[i];
    DATA_TYPE *rowp = A[i+1];
    for (j = 1; j < n-1; ++j) {
      DATA_TYPE s = rowm[j-1] + rowm[j] + rowm[j+1]
                  + row [j-1] + row [j] + row [j+1]
                  + rowp[j-1] + rowp[j] + rowp[j+1];
      row[j] = s * inv9;
    }
  }
}

对 i/j 做二维分块，使活跃工作集尽量停留在 L1/L2。由于是原地更新，块内仍按合法顺序执行。示例：
const int Bi = 32;
const int Bj = 128;
for (t = 0; t < tsteps; ++t)
  for (int ii = 1; ii < n-1; ii += Bi)
    for (int jj = 1; jj < n-1; jj += Bj) {
      int iend = (ii + Bi < n-1) ? ii + Bi : n-1;
      int jend = (jj + Bj < n-1) ? jj + Bj : n-1;
      for (i = ii; i < iend; ++i) {
        DATA_TYPE *rowm = A[i-1];
        DATA_TYPE *row  = A[i];
        DATA_TYPE *rowp = A[i+1];
        for (j = jj; j < jend; ++j) {
          row[j] = (rowm[j-1] + rowm[j] + rowm[j+1]
                  + row [j-1] + row [j] + row [j+1]
                  + rowp[j-1] + rowp[j] + rowp[j+1]) * inv9;
        }
      }
    }
块大小需按元素大小和目标缓存调优。

将 (i,j) 更新按 i+j 的反对角线组织，同一波前上的点彼此独立，可用 OpenMP 并行。示意：
for (t = 0; t < tsteps; ++t) {
  for (int s = 2; s <= 2*(n-2); ++s) {
    int ib = (s-(n-2) > 1) ? s-(n-2) : 1;
    int ie = (s-1 < n-2) ? s-1 : n-2;
    #pragma omp parallel for schedule(static)
    for (int i = ib; i <= ie; ++i) {
      int j = s - i;
      A[i][j] = (A[i-1][j-1] + A[i-1][j] + A[i-1][j+1]
               + A[i][j-1]   + A[i][j]   + A[i][j+1]
               + A[i+1][j-1] + A[i+1][j] + A[i+1][j+1]) * inv9;
    }
  }
}
更高效的实现通常结合菱形分块/时间分块，减少每条波前的同步次数。

若允许改变更新顺序：
1) Jacobi 双缓冲：Anew[i][j] = stencil(Aold)，每步交换指针；可完全并行、易向量化。
2) Red-black：按棋盘染色，两次 sweep 更新红点/黑点，每个颜色内部可并行。
Jacobi 示例：
for (t = 0; t < tsteps; ++t) {
  for (i = 1; i < n-1; ++i) {
    DATA_TYPE *restrict out = B[i];
    DATA_TYPE *restrict rm = A[i-1];
    DATA_TYPE *restrict r  = A[i];
    DATA_TYPE *restrict rp = A[i+1];
    #pragma omp simd
    for (j = 1; j < n-1; ++j)
      out[j] = (rm[j-1]+rm[j]+rm[j+1]+r[j-1]+r[j]+r[j+1]+rp[j-1]+rp[j]+rp[j+1]) * inv9;
  }
  swap(A,B);
}
注意：这会改变数值轨迹，与原始 Seidel 不完全等价。

将二维下标改为一维连续访问，或保留二维但确保编译器可向量化。示例：
for (i = 0; i < n; ++i) {
  DATA_TYPE *row = A[i];
  #pragma omp simd
  for (j = 0; j < n; ++j)
    row[j] = ((DATA_TYPE)i * (j + 2) + 2) / n;
}
若 init 不在 timed region，优化优先级低。
